unittitle_ssm: Giuliano Garavini collection
abstract_ssm: Digital copies, in PDF format, of minutes of conference meetings of the Organization of the Petroleum Exporting Countries (OPEC), and associated documents, from the beginning of the conference in 1960 up to 1986, acquired by historian Giuliano Garavini during the research and writing of his book "The Rise and Fall of OPEC in the Twentieth Century."
corpname_ssm: NYU Abu Dhabi, Archives and Special Collections
heading_ssm: Giuliano Garavini collection
